    <title>Mac配置Hadoop伪分布式环境</title>
    <link href="/2023/02/05/Mac%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEHadoop%E4%BC%AA%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/"/>
    <url>/2023/02/05/Mac%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEHadoop%E4%BC%AA%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p class="note note-warning">⚠️配置Hadoop之前需要提前配置好Java及其环境变量!!!</p><h1>Mac安装Hadoop</h1><p>这里直接使用Homebrew安装Hadoop。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">brew install hadoop<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">查看Hadoop信息</span><br>brew info hadoop<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1>修改配置文件</h1><p>Hadoop伪分布式环境的配置需要修改2个配置文件，分别是：</p><ul><li>core-site.xml</li><li>hdfs-site.xml</li></ul><blockquote><p>这两个配置文件均位于<code>/usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/libexec/etc/hadoop</code>目录下，注意3.3.4需要修改为自己的版本号。</p></blockquote><h2 id="修改core-site-xml">修改core-site.xml</h2><p>修改<strong>configuration</strong>标签内的内容</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">configuration</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>hadoop.tmp.dir<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!--value标签中路径的3.3.4也需要修改为自己的版本号--&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span>file:/usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/libexec/tmp<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">description</span>&gt;</span>Abase for other temporary directories.<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">description</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>fs.defaultFS<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span>hdfs://localhost:9000<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">configuration</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="修改hdfs-site-xml">修改hdfs-site.xml</h2><p>修改<strong>configuration</strong>标签内的内容</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">configuration</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>dfs.replication<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>dfs.namenode.name.dir<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!--value标签中路径的3.3.4也需要修改为自己的版本号--&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span>file:/usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/libexec/tmp/dfs/name<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>dfs.datanode.data.dir<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!--value标签中路径的3.3.4也需要修改为自己的版本号--&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span>file:/usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/libexec/tmp/dfs/data<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">configuration</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1>配置环境变量</h1><p>如果已经配置好Java的环境变量，则可以通过如下命令查看</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">echo $JAVA_HOME<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_351.jdk/Contents/Home/</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以直接在JAVA_HOME的配置文件中添加Hadoop的环境变量</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">3.3.4需要修改为自己的版本号</span><br>export HADOOP_HOME=/usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/libexec<br>export HADOOP_COMMON_LIB_NATIVE_DIR=$HADOOP_HOME/lib/native<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1>配置SSH免密登录</h1><p>在Mac的<strong>系统设置</strong>中找到<strong>共享</strong>，打开<strong>远程登录</strong>选项</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">使用如下命令生成RSA密钥对，一直回车，需要时输入y</span><br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -P &quot;&quot;<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">进入~/.ssh目录</span><br>cd ~/.ssh<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">将公钥内容写入authorized_keys文件</span><br>cat id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; ~/.ssh/authorized_keys<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">验证SSH是否可以免密登录</span><br>ssh localhost<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果没有报错并且不需要输入密码就进入了新的Shell，则免密登录配置成功。</p><hr><h1>启动Hadoop</h1><h2 id="初始化Hadoop">初始化Hadoop</h2><p>首次启动需要初始化namenode。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">cd /usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/bin<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">初始化namenode</span><br>./hdfs namenode -format<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="运行Hadoop">运行Hadoop</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">cd /usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/sbin<br>./start-dfs.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里可能出现的问题很多，如果报错，可以对照输出结果排查一下。</p><h2 id="检查启动是否成功">检查启动是否成功</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">检查相关进程是否已经启动</span><br>jps -l<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">正常情况下，NameNode、SecondaryNameNode、DataNode都应该启动</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">38034 org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.datanode.DataNode</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">38297 jdk.jcmd/sun.tools.jps.Jps</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">38170 org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode.SecondaryNameNode</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">37932 org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode.NameNode</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在浏览器输入<code>localhost:9870</code>查看namenode<br><img src="https://blog-img-1312725637.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/article4/NameNode.png" alt="" title="NameNode页面"></p><h2 id="如果配置成功，应该显示如上的页面。">如果配置成功，应该显示如上的页面。</h2><h1>配置并启动Yarn</h1><h2 id="配置Yarn">配置Yarn</h2><p>Yarn的配置需要修改两个配置文件：</p><ul><li>mapred-site.xml</li><li>yarn-site.xml</li></ul><blockquote><p>这两个配置文件均位于/usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/libexec/etc/hadoop目录下</p></blockquote><h3 id="修改mapred-site-xml">修改mapred-site.xml</h3><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">configuration</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>mapreduce.framework.name<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span>yarn<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">configuration</span>&gt;</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="修改yarn-site-xml">修改yarn-site.xml</h3><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">configuration</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>yarn.nodemanager.aux-services<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span>mapreduce_shuffle<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br>       <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>yarn.nodemanager.env-whitelist<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>      <br>       <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span>JAVA_HOME,HADOOP_COMMON_HOME,HADOOP_HDFS_HOME,HADOOP_CONF_DIR,CLASSPATH_PREPEND_DISTCACHE,HADOOP_YARN_HOME,HADOOP_MAPRED_HOME<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">value</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">property</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">configuration</span>&gt;</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="启动Yarn">启动Yarn</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">cd /usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/sbin<br>./start-yarn.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在浏览器输入localhost:8088</p><p><img src="https://blog-img-1312725637.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/article4/Hadoop%20Cluster.png" alt="Hadoop集群页面" title="Hadoop集群页面"><br>如果上述配置和启动没有问题，应该显示如上页面。</p><p class="note note-primary">配置完成，完结撒花🎉</p><hr><h1>关闭服务</h1><p>在start-dfs.sh文件的同目录(/usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/sbin)下有stop-dfs.sh等文件，通过执行stop文件即可关闭对应的服务。</p><blockquote><p>通过start-all.sh和stop-all.sh文件可以一次性开启/关闭所有服务。</p></blockquote><hr><h1>报错解决</h1><h2 id="关于Hadoop本地库">关于Hadoop本地库</h2><p>在配置过程中，可能会出现如下警告⚠️</p><p><code>WARN util.NativeCodeLoader: Unable to load native-hadoop library for your platform... using builtin-java classes where applicable</code></p><p>native-hadoop不支持Mac OS，因此可以跳过这个警告。</p><h2 id="NameNode初始化报错">NameNode初始化报错</h2><p>我在初始化NameNode时出现了如下报错：</p><p><code>JAVA_HOME @@HOMEBREW_JAVA@@ does not exist</code></p><p>查阅另一篇blog发现是因为hadoop-env.sh文件中的JAVA_HOME没有配置正确的原因。(该文件位于/usr/local/Cellar/hadoop/3.3.4/libexec/etc/hadoop目录下)</p><p>将该文件中的JAVA_HOME配置为<strong>本机的JAVA_HOME</strong>即可。</p><hr><p>参考：<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44570264/article/details/106872445">mac安装hadoop及配置伪分布式</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45048331/article/details/109822493">ERROR: JAVA_HOME /usr/lib/jvm/default-java does not exist. 运行Hadoop出现</a><br><a href="https://hadoop.apache.org/docs/r1.0.4/cn/native_libraries.html">Hadoop本地库</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
